We have developed an ergonomic and modern interface, filling the application with only the necessary functions..

Using the application, you can::

- keep records of expenses and income without spending a lot of time on it
- keep a record of all your transactions and view them at any time;
- choose a currency that is convenient for you;
- view changes in any currency exchange rate on the charts;
- distribute operations and expenses according to criteria;
- create your own categories for the distribution of operations.

Analyze your expenses, record and track transactions and increase your capital - it does not require a lot of time and effort!

